data.description: Motivated Seller! Nestled within the serene Brookstone subdivision in Clearwater, Florida, this beautifully updated 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom pool home beckons you to embrace the epitome of comfortable, modern living. As you enter the home through the double front doors you are welcomed with vaulted ceilings throughout. This move in ready home is meticulously prepared for its new owners to settle in effortlessly. The living room welcomes you with the warmth of a fireplace, creating a cozy ambiance for relaxation and a beautiful built-in bar for gatherings. The kitchen features solid wood cabinets, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, custom backsplash, and a designer faucet. Step into the oversized primary bedroom, a serene haven featuring direct access to the covered lanai and pool area. This retreat offers a walk-in closet and a stunning bathroom adorned with a soaker tub and a separate shower, providing a touch of opulence and tranquility. The spacious second and third bedrooms located on the opposite side of the home, offer versatility and comfort, catering to the needs of family or guests. Entertain or unwind in the private pool area, a haven of relaxation and leisure set within your own backyard. Enjoy the convenience of being situated in the highly sought-after Brookstone subdivision, offering easy access to Clearwater's amenities, beautiful beaches, and a vibrant array of dining, shopping, and entertainment options. Experience the epitome of luxury living in Clearwater. Schedule a viewing today and envision the lifestyle awaiting you in this exceptional turnkey property.  Updates/Upgrades Include: Whole House Water Filtration System, 2022 Water Heater, 2020 Roof, 2023 Pool was resurfaced & retiled, 2023 Pool Deck was repainted, 2023 New pool pump, Newer windows, 2022 A/C & Handler.
